Barroso Says European Union, Euro at ‘Crucial Point’

-- B y   P a t r i c k   H e n r y
-- 
2011-10-19T10:49:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-19/barroso-says-european-union-euro-at-crucial-point-.html
European Commission President  Jose
Barroso  said the European Union and the single currency are at
“a crucial moment, a crucial point.”  “We’re at a very, very sensitive point in European
construction,” Barroso told reporters in Brussels today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
